snippet.title: President Obama Roasts Donald Trump At Whcd 2016 White House Correspondents Dinner

localized.description:
President Obama Roasts Donald Trump At Whcd 2016 White House Correspondents Dinner. On Saturday night, April 30, 2016, Larry Wilmore hosts the White House Correspondents’ Association Dinner live from Washington, D.C. President Barack Obama will deliver his seventh speech at the annual event, which will begin at approximately 7:30 p.m. ET. 2016 White House Correspondents' Dinner Journalists, politicians, and celebrities gathered for the White House Correspondents' Association annual dinner. President Obama and comedian Larry Wilmore made humorous remarks about politics and the media.
